-- Bugs Fixed and Ready For Release 
Fixed: Player tooltips on plan dialog don't work
Fixed: Auto defense dialog refreshing when other players use theirs
Fixed: Compilation problems due to std namespace being global
Fixed: Some MSVC 2003 compilation problems
Fixed: Buoys now shaded

Added: Bot names can be randomly choosen by setting config option
Added: All effects speed up with increased speed settings
Added: Can change secondary camera windows view (by clicking on camera type)
Added: Tank models can be made larger (does not effect other clients or damage radius)
Added: Action camera now shows view from behind tank during turn
Added: Server file logging is off by default
Added: Tooltips to display settings and server dialogs
Added: Fail safe for actions that time them out after 30 seconds

-- Bugs in current development release
Dvorak keyboard support is broken
The server can start multiple times on the same port (windows only)!
Gun fires at same point for all tanks (ignores turret/gun position in model)
Shot cam does not get LOD correctly

